    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "噛み噛みすずにゃん様も可愛い～！",
      "startTime": 50.9666653871,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "からかわないでくださいまし！\nそれより、クイズ大会は楽しめましたの？",
      "startTime": 57.5503813667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん様に関する問題、面白かったー！\n雫ちゃん全問正解おめでとう！",
      "startTime": 65.633329765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "……ぶい\nすずちゃん様のことなら、任せて……",
      "startTime": 70.8666671674,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　すずにゃん様！　星見プロのみんなから\n沢山のプレゼントが届いてるみたいだよ！",
      "startTime": 78.1000005007,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "象は呼べなかったけど、クマなら……ある",
      "startTime": 83.1501089811,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "こんなにもらっていいんですの！？\n全部、私に……？",
      "startTime": 89.9921927378,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ！　ぜーんぶすずにゃん様へのプレゼント！\nそれじゃあ、雫ちゃん、いくよ！　せーのっ……",
      "startTime": 97.7999943973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃん様、お誕生日、おめでと～～～！",
      "startTime": 102.7683333319,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3431.664371400004,
          "startTime": 106.1999977033
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、雫……っ！　そしてファンのみなさん……っ\n心より感謝を申し上げます……私は、幸せ者ですわ！",
      "startTime": 116.1756133642,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "今日は……本当に……っ\n最高の誕生日ですわ～～！",
      "startTime": 127.275612347,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1209.061510799998,
          "startTime": 128.4846738578
        }
      ]
    },
    {
