      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "みなさんからの祝福、今日は沢山受け取りました\nこの勢いで、私……成宮すずは――",
      "startTime": 138.2089466976,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6424.384338999999,
          "startTime": 144.6333310366
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルの天下を取りますわ！",
      "startTime": 143.3213682891,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "……でも今日で、取ったも同然……\nすでに、天下はすずにゃん様の手にあり……です",
      "startTime": 149.3666539432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、別の目標が必要かも？\nすずにゃん様、世界一のアイドルに！　ってどうかな？",
      "startTime": 158.1333206099,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "素晴らしいですわ！\n目標は大きいほどいいのです。それでは――",
      "startTime": 165.0739704696,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "私、成宮すずは……\n世界一、いえ、宇宙一のアイドルになりますわ！",
      "startTime": 172.2406371363,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "よっ！　さすが宇宙一のすずにゃん様～！\nトップアイドルの上の上の上だよ～！",
      "startTime": 182.1333165409,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-szk007.m4a",
      "text": "まさに、「ここから宇宙へ」……\n何もかも、超えていく存在……",
      "startTime": 189.1666478398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_51_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "ええ！\nこの成宮すずに超えられないものなどありません！",
      "startTime": 192.7561570098,
      "sfxList": [
